              "free_text": [
                " The resonance strength of the",
                "level at 448 keV in 20Na vas studied in inverse",
                "kinematics via the 19Ne(p,g)20Na reaction. A",
                "radioactive 19Ne (charge state: 3+) beam with energy",
                "of 9.8 MeV was directed at a 80 ug/cm2 thick CH2",
                "target. The 20Na nuclei from the reaction were",
                "identified with the ARES recoil separator."
              ]
            }
          ],
